data.description: SELLER OFFERING $5K BUYER INCENTIVE! This home offers a combination of elegance, comfort, and modern amenities. The spacious floor plan boasts a warm and inviting atmosphere with stylish finishes throughout. The open-concept living area seamlessly connects the living room, dining area and kitchen. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, laminate countertops, and custom cabinetry. The primary suite is a private retreat with a spacious bedroom, offering lots of natural lighting. Additional bedrooms are well-appointed and versatile. The backyard includes a covered patio and a nice size yard for outdoor activities. Other features include a two-car garage and storage shed in the backyard. The property lis located in a charming neighborhood with convenient access to HWY 190, shopping, dining, and schools. Contact us now to schedule your private showing. Full interior carpet replacement allowance offered.
